data.description: Discover luxury living in this spacious 6-bedroom, 3-full bath home spanning 3,078 square feet in the exclusive gated community of Hawks Point, Ruskin, Florida. Nestled by a serene pond, this residence offers a tranquil retreat. The kitchen and bathrooms boast elegant tile flooring, while plush carpeting graces the bedrooms for added comfort. The living room features modern luxury vinyl plank (LVP) flooring, creating a seamless blend of style and practicality. Enjoy the scenic pond views from your private backyard, perfect for entertaining or unwinding. With a prime location in Hawks Point, residents benefit from community amenities and a secure, welcoming atmosphere. Don't miss the chance to make this exquisite property your dream home. Schedule a showing today and experience the epitome of Florida living in this meticulously maintained residence.
